The paper deals with graph theory and combinatorics, specifically the intersection of tolerance and cocomparability graphs. This topic falls under several arXiv CS sub-categories, including Discrete Mathematics (cs.DM), Data Structures and Algorithms (cs.DS), Computational Geometry (cs.CG), Graph Theory (cs.GT), and Logic in Computer Science (cs.LG). However, since the paper focuses on graph theory and combinatorics, cs.DM and cs.DS are the most likely sub-categories. The paper also involves constructive proofs and conjectures, which may suggest a connection to cs.LG.
